  "detailed_description": "<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Build! </h2></strong><br><br>You will find 29 types of buildings, each of which produces goods and participates in the life of your country. Build production chains to produce complex goods<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/e3d32b6caa742de1163130bee092f58f.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Develop your lands! </h2></strong><br><br>You have to create a state from scratch, starting with one detachment of settlers. Gradually, you will grow, develop, and become stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/251b0dc77175fe231b3537b42c03d92b.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=890 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Resources! </h2></strong><br><br>There are 25 types of resources in the game. Food is consumed by the population, materials are needed for construction and complex production, and weapons are needed for soldiers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/5ac2bebcee6db864b2cc14c3f5736d7e.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Divide and Conquer! </h2></strong><br><br>The game has an advanced diplomacy system. Make alliances, fight, fuel discontent, invest. Prove that you are a worthy ruler!<br><br>If there is no gain, do not move; if you cannot gain, do not use troops; if there is no danger, do not fight. The sovereign should not take up arms because of his anger; the commander should not engage in battle because of his anger.<br><i>(C) Sun Tzu</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/3a4c4eebefdd17907df9982d81bd8188.poster.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/3a4c4eebefdd17907df9982d81bd8188.webm?t=1753025556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/3a4c4eebefdd17907df9982d81bd8188.mp4?t=1753025556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Technologies! </h2></strong><br><br>117 technologies and 4 conditional stages of society development are waiting for you: Tribal system, feudalism, capitalism, industrialism.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/6cc511595e4faf24abcbd60d20a6199c.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Develop economy! </h2></strong><br><br>Keep track of the parameters of your economy. Build production, allocate resources, subsidize private business. The game combines simplicity and depth of economy. Become successful!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/b8484eda71d3086817338ec2d561ac48.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Build! </h2></strong><br><br>You will find 29 types of buildings, each of which produces goods and participates in the life of your country. Build production chains to produce complex goods<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/e3d32b6caa742de1163130bee092f58f.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Develop your lands! </h2></strong><br><br>You have to create a state from scratch, starting with one detachment of settlers. Gradually, you will grow, develop, and become stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/251b0dc77175fe231b3537b42c03d92b.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=890 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Resources! </h2></strong><br><br>There are 25 types of resources in the game. Food is consumed by the population, materials are needed for construction and complex production, and weapons are needed for soldiers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/5ac2bebcee6db864b2cc14c3f5736d7e.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Divide and Conquer! </h2></strong><br><br>The game has an advanced diplomacy system. Make alliances, fight, fuel discontent, invest. Prove that you are a worthy ruler!<br><br>If there is no gain, do not move; if you cannot gain, do not use troops; if there is no danger, do not fight. The sovereign should not take up arms because of his anger; the commander should not engage in battle because of his anger.<br><i>(C) Sun Tzu</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/3a4c4eebefdd17907df9982d81bd8188.poster.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/3a4c4eebefdd17907df9982d81bd8188.webm?t=1753025556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/3a4c4eebefdd17907df9982d81bd8188.mp4?t=1753025556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Technologies! </h2></strong><br><br>117 technologies and 4 conditional stages of society development are waiting for you: Tribal system, feudalism, capitalism, industrialism.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/6cc511595e4faf24abcbd60d20a6199c.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Develop economy! </h2></strong><br><br>Keep track of the parameters of your economy. Build production, allocate resources, subsidize private business. The game combines simplicity and depth of economy. Become successful!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847600/extras/b8484eda71d3086817338ec2d561ac48.avif?t=1753025556\" width=570 height=314 /></span>",
